1. Ona je prezadovoljna njime. (*Njime*) (She is very satisfied with it.) 
2. On je zadovoljan svojim rezultatima, ali njime ne. (*Njime*) (He is satisfied with his results, but not with it.) 
3. Nastojali smo da ispunimo svoje obaveze bez pomoći njime. (*Njime*) (We tried to fulfill our obligations without its help.) 
4. On je upotrebio njime da bi došao do svoje celi. (*Njime*) (He used it to get to his goal.) 
5. On se zakleo da će zaštititi svoje blago od njime. (*Njime*) (He swore to protect his treasure from it.)